data.details: Join us at North Fork Leadership Center and complete activities from "It's Your Story - Tell it!" Journey Series! Make new friends, have fun and explore a Journey that's all about discovering what's great in the world around us. Cost includes a snack, take home and lots of hands on activities. The GS Store will be on site. Adult Leaders will also have a special breakout session to learn how to incoporate what they have seen into their troop setting. This event costs $10 per girl and $6 per adult.
